' =============================================================================
' GTNH Platform — User Flow: Multiblocks
' 3 диаграммы: EBF, Large Boiler, Large Chemical Reactor
' =============================================================================

' ===========================================================================
' 1. Electric Blast Furnace (EBF)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml multiblock-ebf
title **Flow MB1: Electric Blast Furnace (EBF)**

actor "Игрок" as Player
participant "GameClient" as Client
participant "SimulationCore" as Sim
participant "ChunkStore" as CS
participant "RecipeManager" as RM
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "EntityStateStore" as ESS
participant "SpatialIndex" as SI

== Сборка EBF ==

Player -> Client: Ставит блоки по паттерну 3х3х4
note right #9B59B6
  EBF Pattern (3x3x4):
  Layer 0: [ C C C ] - касинг
           [ C C C ]
           [ C C C ]
  Layer 1: [ C A C ] - A = air
           [ A H A ] - H = heating coil
           [ C A C ]
  Layer 2: (same as 1)
  Layer 3: [ C C C ]
           [ C M C ] - M = controller / muffler
           [ C C C ]

  Всего: 34 блока касинга (casings)
         2 слота для катушек (heating coils)
         Контроллер (EBF Controller)
         Muffler hatch наверху
end note

== Detection: каждый SetBlock ==

Client -> Sim: SetBlockAction (каждый блок)
Sim -> CS: SetBlock CAS

Sim -> Sim: onBlockChanged(pos, block_id)

Sim -> SI: FindPattern(pos)
note right #9B59B6
  SpatialIndex проверяет:
  - Все блоки вокруг pos
  - Сравнивает с EBF pattern
  - Если совпало: MultiblockController
end note

alt Pattern match: EBF complete
    Sim -> Sim: Create MultiblockController ECS entity
    Sim -> Sim: Find all hatches (input, output, energy, muffler)

    Sim -> CS: SetBlockMeta для всех блоков\n(запись mb_id в meta-layer)
    Sim -> ESS: Save multiblock state (hatches, coils, tier)

    Sim -> MR: Publish sim.multiblock.created
    Client -> Player: EBF активен!

    == EBF tick (20 Hz) ==

    Sim -> Sim: Tick: EBF running

    Sim -> RM: FindRecipe(ebf_id, input_items, heat_required)
    RM --> Sim: Recipe found (requires 1800K heat)

    Sim -> PN: CheckEnergy(ebf_id, eu_cost/tick)
    PN --> Sim: Energy OK

    Sim -> Sim: Check coil heat capacity
    note right: Kanhal (1800K), Nichrome (2700K),\nTungstenSteel (4500K)\nCoil tier определяет max heat

    alt Heat >= recipe_heat_required
        Sim -> Sim: Advance recipe progress
        alt Recipe complete
            Sim -> Sim: Consume inputs, produce outputs
            Sim -> ESS: Save output to hatches
        end
    else Heat < required
        Sim -> Sim: Pause, heat too low
    end
else Pattern not complete
    Sim -> Sim: Single blocks only (no multiblock)
end

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 2. Large Steam Boiler
' ===========================================================================
@startuml multiblock-large-boiler
title **Flow MB2: Large Steam Boiler**

actor "Игрок" as Player
participant "SimulationCore" as Sim
participant "RecipeManager" as RM
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "ChunkStore" as CS
participant "EntityStateStore" as ESS

== Сборка парогенератора ==

Player -> Client: Ставит блоки Large Boiler

note right #5899DA
  Large Boiler (3x3x4):
  - Controller + касинг
  - Firebox (для горения)
  - Water intake hatches
  - Steam output hatches
  - Размеры: 1x1x1 -> 3x3x4 (LP -> HP)
end note

== Detection ==

Sim -> Sim: onBlockChanged -> pattern match

alt Pattern match: boiler complete
    Sim -> Sim: Create MultiblockController
    Sim -> CS: SetBlockMeta (mb_id)
    Sim -> MR: Publish sim.multiblock.created

    == Boiler tick ==

    Tick -> Sim: tick(dt)

    Sim -> Sim: Check fuel in firebox inventory
    note right: Топливо: coal, charcoal,\nили жидкое топливо

    alt Has fuel
        Sim -> Sim: Burn fuel, generate heat
        Sim -> Sim: Check water in input hatch

        alt Has water
            Sim -> Sim: Convert water -> steam
            Sim -> PN: Publish fluid.node.update
            PN -> PN: Distribute steam to network
        else No water
            Sim -> Sim: Heat buildup (overheat risk)
        end
    else No fuel
        Sim -> Sim: Cool down, no steam
    end

    Sim -> ESS: Save boiler state (heat, fuel, water)
end

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 3. Large Chemical Reactor (LCR)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml multiblock-lcr
title **Flow MB3: Large Chemical Reactor (LCR)**

actor "Игрок" as Player
participant "SimulationCore" as Sim
participant "RecipeManager" as RM
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "ChunkStore" as CS
participant "EntityStateStore" as ESS

== Сборка LCR ==

Player -> Client: Ставит блоки LCR

note right #E67E22
  LCR Pattern:
  - 3x3x3 касинг
  - Внутри пусто (air / fluid)
  - Controller спереди
  - Input/Output hatches
  - Energy hatch
  - Fluid hatches для жидкостей
end note

== Detection + Activation ==

Sim -> Sim: onBlockChanged -> pattern match
Sim -> Sim: Create MultiblockController

== LCR tick ==

Sim -> Sim: Tick(dt)

Sim -> RM: FindRecipe(lcr_id, inputs)
note right #E67E22
  LCR рецепты:
  - Требуют жидкости + предметы
  - Chemical reactions
  - Например: sulfuric_acid + iron -> iron_sulfate
  - Требуют EU/t
end note

RM --> Sim: Recipe found

Sim -> PN: CheckEnergy(lcr_id, eu_cost/tick)
PN --> Sim: Energy available

Sim -> Sim: Check fluid inputs
note right: Fluid hatches содержат\nнеобходимые жидкости

alt All inputs satisfied
    Sim -> Sim: Advance recipe
    Sim -> PN: ConsumeEnergy(eu_cost/tick)
    Sim -> PN: ConsumeFluid(input_fluids)

    alt Recipe complete
        Sim -> Sim: Output items + fluids to hatches
        Sim -> ESS: Save LCR state
        Sim -> MR: Publish machine.state.updated
    end
else Missing inputs
    Sim -> Sim: Idle, wait for materials
end

== Multiblocks: общий lifecycle ==

note right #9B59B6
  Multiblocks:
  - SimulationCore ECS: MultiblockController entity
  - Components: MachineComponent + EnergyStorage + InventoryContainer + SideConfig
  - persisted через EntityStateStore
  - Обнаружение через onBlockChanged + SpatialIndex
  - L2 deferred в BFS анализе
end note

@enduml
